title: Round Rock neighborhood decks out for the Fourth

track.imageLink: http://statesman.com/photogallery/Round Rock neighborhood decks out for the Fourth/

items.caption: Grace Coghlan at the wheel of Dave and Suzanne Waeltermann's well-decorated four-wheeler. The Greater Round Rock West Neighborhood Association held its annual Fourth of July Parade, as a no-walking event for COVID-19 safety, on July 4, 2020. [Henry Huey for Statesman.]
